<div style="
    background-color: #007bff!important;     
    font-family: 'Roboto Slab', serif;;
    margin-right: 15px;
    margin-left: 15px;
    padding:15px;
    text-align: center!important;
    color: #f8f9fa!important;
    ">
<h5 style="font-size:3rem;padding:0px;margin:0px">WDYLT</h5>
<h5 style="font-size:0.7rem;margin-top:0px">what did you learn today</h5>
</div>

<div style="
    font-family: 'Roboto Slab', serif;;
    margin-right: 15px;
    margin-left: 15px;
    padding:15px;
    text-align: center!important;
    color: #007bff!important;
    ">
Congrats on another week of growth! </br></br><span style="font-size:1 rem;">Take 10-20 minutes and summarize your learnings from the week</span> 

<a href="http://www.get-wdylt.com/new_reflection" style="font-family: 'Roboto Slab', serif;    display: block;
    width: 75%;    padding: .5rem 1rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    border-radius: .3rem;font-weight: 400;
    text-align: center;
    white-space: nowrap;
    vertical-align: middle;border: 1px solid transparent; background-color: #007bff; margin:auto;margin-top:15px;color:f8f9fa;">Reflect now.</a>   

</div>


<div style="
    background-color: #007bff!important;     
    font-family: 'Roboto Slab', serif;;
    margin-right: 15px;
    margin-left: 15px;
    padding:15px;
    text-align: center!important;
    color: #f8f9fa!important;
    ">
<h5 style="font-size:1rem;padding:0px;margin:0px">Here's everything you've learned since the last time you reflected:</h5>
</div>
<% if @user_responses.count != 0%>
<% @user_responses.each do |response| %>

    
    
    
    
    <div style="position: relative;
        display: -ms-flexbox;
        display: flex;
        -ms-flex-direction: column;
        flex-direction: column;
        min-width: 0;
        word-wrap: break-word;
        background-color: #fff;
        background-clip: border-box;
        border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.125);
        border-radius: .25rem;
        margin-left:15px;
        margin-right:15px;
        margin-bottom:3px;
        margin-top:3px;
        padding:5px;
    ">
    
    <div stye="
        font-size: 80%;
        font-family: sans-serif;
    ">
        <% t = response.created_at.in_time_zone(@user.time_zone) %>
        <small class="card-text text-right"><%=t.strftime("%A, %B %-d, %Y: %l:%M %p %Z")%></small>
        
        
    </div>
           <p><%=response.response_text%></p>
    </div>
<% end %>
<% end %>
